Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.73,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.44,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.42,0:00:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.19,0:00:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.67,0:00:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.15,0:01:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.75,0:01:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.19,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.23,0:01:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.77,0:01:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.50,0:01:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你金榜題名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.96,0:01:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.83,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上了大學之後請穿穿看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.29,0:03:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#05響子焦慮不安!五代離家出走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代還沒回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經一個禮拜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為現在是落榜通知的季節嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你們老是欺負他的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才沒有欺負他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.58,0:03:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是實話實說罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這明明就是在欺負他嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過真叫人擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟在這種時期…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等他全都落榜以後\N就會回來了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總不能這樣一直逃避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.31,0:04:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要是沒考上一所大學\N我就回不了一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.45,0:04:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說你打算在我那裡\N賴到明年嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上來開燒肉派對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰跟你吃燒肉啊\N內褲比較重要,內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內褲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來開燒肉派對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,我要買新的內褲來穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你\N你現在寄住在誰的家裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.95,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借我一條內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種東西怎麼可以借人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些東西是我贏來的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豬頭,要內褲回家拿不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑰匙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.71,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.77,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像玩得很開心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是新的遊戲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.94,0:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦,內…內褲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四…四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考生莫名墜樓死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑似受不了聯考之苦而自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,好像不是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他也太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.93,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要外宿的話\N至少也打通電話來不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,這個怎麼來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(投幣式自助洗衣店)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來我要用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒穿內褲對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.90,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個老太婆真誇張\N這已經是第五盒了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.44,0:10:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你是五代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什麼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.65,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家擔心到連飯都吃不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之快點回來吧\N大家都在等你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問,你是五代吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…妳是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是一刻館的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是五代的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝招待,吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的孫子平時承蒙妳照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.98,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才常常受到五代的照顧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…是我孫子受妳照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…是我受五代的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼這麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳實在太客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,老太婆,碗公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N讓妳提這麼重的行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為裕作會來接我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我孫子的名字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考生的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他的名字不叫重考生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個小鬼也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩三天前信就應該已經寄到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他居然沒有來接我\N搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩三天前\N他怎麼可能看得到明信片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再讓我住幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過你這樣好嗎?\N什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少要跟管理員連絡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟我提到她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經習慣\N被朱美跟四谷他們嘲笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到管理員同情憐憫的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這實在太慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,很慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是慘兮兮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慘到谷底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要重複說啦\N這樣會覺得越來越慘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走…走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代找到了沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位是五代的奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳用不著這麼大聲\N我聽得到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也進來喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上就去,請妳先進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真的是五代的奶奶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.22,0:14:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以請暫時不要在她面前\N提起五代的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道她遲早會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我不想讓\N剛到這裡沒多久的奶奶擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就會穿幫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,只要天黑之前\N把他找回來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想說的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請節哀順變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作全部都落榜了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是時間的問題…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以,這一個禮拜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好啊,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是多此一舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,把她弄哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他逃走了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙會做什麼事\N我大概心裡有數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.24,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙沒什麼毅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只是裝得很煩惱的樣子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶都這麼說了,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我又沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.49,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一刻館的房客太冷漠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔心五代的\N只有管理員一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係,他說的是實話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你們話中帶刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.57,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代不在這裡的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候放榜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是最後一所私立大學放榜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國立大學早就放榜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.25,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國立的根本考不上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天的放榜是關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果明天也落榜的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.93,0:17:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就把裕作帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是當然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.27,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是那種有錢人家\N可以養光吃白飯的重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後沒有消遣對象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,還讓妳陪我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說,希望他能考上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.78,0:17:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想看到孫子哭喪的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.89,0:18:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了…\N好棒喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,到底怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.96,0:18:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道他的准考證號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,人山人海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣什麼都看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等人潮退了再來看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋,我沒有那麼悠哉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,有沒有看到?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.34,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起喔\N裕作應該會來看榜才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上去囉,五代\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,阪本,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話,快點看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,五代,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追啊,快追!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶和管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,為什麼奶奶會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底有沒有考上?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說啊說啊,到底有沒有考上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒看啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個沒出息的傢伙\N到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.68,0:20:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要打我啦\N頭殼會被妳打壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.35,0:20:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人潮好像少了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.29,0:21:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,不要跳了啦,太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.35,0:22:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,不要跳了啦,太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全跟不上他們的步調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.13,0:22:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚大概會被他們牽著走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.46,0:22:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.70,0:22:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這樣也很好啊\N有人讓我們繼續消遣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.17,0:22:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為五代是我的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.61,0:22:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,大家請儘量喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天特別寬待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.38,0:22:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要幹什麼?\N放開我!放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.73,0:22:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.33,0:22:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.74,0:22:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.94,0:22:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經洗乾淨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.11,0:22:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.68,0:22:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.45,0:23:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊對啊,什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.02,0:23:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.15,0:23:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裕作,你又幹了什麼好事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奶奶,妳誤會了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的沒有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.96,0:23:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼到底是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.63,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不是你們想像的那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想像的是什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.80,0:23:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝吧,管理員,喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.27,0:23:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就盡情地喝吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.87,0:23:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶,喝個痛快,喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.28,0:23:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.15,0:23:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.57,0:23:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代考上了大學\N一刻館的春天也終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.81,0:23:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過櫻花的季節\N對我來說是很難受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.24,0:24:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回\N『春天的衝擊!響子的秘密!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.72,0:24:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,這個下個禮拜再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.07,0:24:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.38,0:24:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.52,0:24:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.42,0:24:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.66,0:24:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.20,0:25:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.64,0:25:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
